  "detailed_description": "<h1>Welcome to the Animal Crusaders！</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/582480c35e2f2b672b0b43b367f5d617.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Check, check, this is Warcluck speaking，Join us on this journey to save the world! Your feedback will help us make it even better.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bilibili: @黑灯游戏  Heybox:@黑灯游戏  森空岛:@黑灯游戏 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/05615da89cd80a61aa2d947cad151f23.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=335 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/25614547ea48ffe01b47cfc19685eba3.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/787fd03576cc7d97a0c3991bc0211e28.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Cluckmechs, endless combinations.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity with over 100 defensive structures and 300+ upgrade paths! Combine different towers and upgrades to create unique and powerful strategies. The possibilities are truly endless!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/b02b66a3bd6615eccf21ff37847171c0.poster.avif?t=1773213112\" width=572 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/b02b66a3bd6615eccf21ff37847171c0.webm?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/b02b66a3bd6615eccf21ff37847171c0.mp4?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/bec61ab4ada1ff335ca2051bed60462e.poster.avif?t=1773213112\" width=572 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/bec61ab4ada1ff335ca2051bed60462e.webm?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/bec61ab4ada1ff335ca2051bed60462e.mp4?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/912b55e1d209a953ef48a6051fbfb0c9.poster.avif?t=1773213112\" width=572 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/912b55e1d209a953ef48a6051fbfb0c9.webm?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/912b55e1d209a953ef48a6051fbfb0c9.mp4?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/440bed238639bda0394fcbf8cc585b39.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoy fast-paced and addictive gameplay with a wide range of characters and abilities.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the firepower of the Warcluck to the trap-laying expertise of the Mouscle, each Character has unique skills and tactics.  With endless replayability, build and upgrade your defenses, lead your troops, and defeat waves of enemies. Choose from a variety of unique heroes and discover new strategies with each playthrough.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/c3e74ee5892d74f2748f765728923382.poster.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/c3e74ee5892d74f2748f765728923382.webm?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/51872c1e87c70c002a76275f71306608.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unleash your creativity then outsmart your enemies with clever strategies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy complete freedom to place your defenses and base anywhere on the map. Strategically plan your enemy's route and build your defenses accordingly.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/5df8c44296acd10da8962a2ed26e093e.poster.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/5df8c44296acd10da8962a2ed26e093e.webm?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/57fd1dd0baea1fe63fc91e9fa34e6c59.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unpredictable adventures, full of wacky humor and unexpected twists.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Embark on a journey filled with humor and wonder, explore unpredictable landscapes and encounter bizarre creatures.  From deserts to glaciers, you'll never know what awaits you. Discover a wacky animal world and hidden surprises at every turn! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/a9b999f80bec85e2b2a9e3f3a9c8a556.poster.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/a9b999f80bec85e2b2a9e3f3a9c8a556.webm?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/f8d52826a0960c711499280a53e7ca8e.poster.avif?t=1773213112\" width=600 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453360/extras/f8d52826a0960c711499280a53e7ca8e.webm?t=1773213112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
